{
  "video_id": "VbF2KPn3TrU",
  "title": "Ellen 't Hoen: Pool medical patents, save lives",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16526.0,
      "end_time": 21150.0,
      "text": "In 2002, a group of treatment activists met"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21150.0,
      "end_time": 25450.0,
      "text": "to discuss the early development of the airplane."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25450.0,
      "end_time": 29746.0,
      "text": "The Wright Brothers, in the beginning of the last century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29746.0,
      "end_time": 31448.0,
      "text": "had for the first time managed"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31448.0,
      "end_time": 34200.0,
      "text": "to make one of those devices fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34200.0,
      "end_time": 37283.0,
      "text": "They also had taken out numerous patents"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37283.0,
      "end_time": 39259.0,
      "text": "on essential parts of the airplane."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39259.0,
      "end_time": 40700.0,
      "text": "They were not the only ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40700.0,
      "end_time": 44284.0,
      "text": "That was common practice in the industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44284.0,
      "end_time": 46576.0,
      "text": "and those who held patents on airplanes"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46576.0,
      "end_time": 47732.0,
      "text": "were defending them fiercely"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47732.0,
      "end_time": 51154.0,
      "text": "and suing competitors left and right."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51154.0,
      "end_time": 56710.0,
      "text": "This actually wasn&#39;t so great for the development of the aviation industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56710.0,
      "end_time": 59376.0,
      "text": "and this was at a time that in particular the U.S. government"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59377.0,
      "end_time": 61934.0,
      "text": "was interested in ramping up"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61934.0,
      "end_time": 64622.0,
      "text": "the production of military airplanes."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64623.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67334.0,
      "text": "So there was a bit of a conflict there."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67334.0,
      "end_time": 70573.0,
      "text": "The U.S. government decided to take action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70573.0,
      "end_time": 72904.0,
      "text": "and forced those patent holders"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72905.0,
      "end_time": 77660.0,
      "text": "to make their patents available to share with others"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77660.0,
      "end_time": 82575.0,
      "text": "to enable the production of airplanes."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82575.0,
      "end_time": 85545.0,
      "text": "So what has this"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85545.0,
      "end_time": 89565.0,
      "text": "got to do with this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89565.0,
      "end_time": 94628.0,
      "text": "In 2002, Nelson Otwoma, a Kenyan social scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94628.0,
      "end_time": 99769.0,
      "text": "discovered he had HIV and needed access to treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99769.0,
      "end_time": 104400.0,
      "text": "He was told that a cure did not exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 104400.0,
      "end_time": 107207.0,
      "text": "AIDS, he heard, was lethal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 107207.0,
      "end_time": 110399.0,
      "text": "and treatment was not offered. This was at a time"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110400.0,
      "end_time": 113168.0,
      "text": "that treatment actually existed in rich countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113168.0,
      "end_time": 116163.0,
      "text": "AIDS had become a chronic disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 116163.0,
      "end_time": 119764.0,
      "text": "People in our countries here in Europe, in North America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119764.0,
      "end_time": 122708.0,
      "text": "were living with HIV, healthy lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122709.0,
      "end_time": 125544.0,
      "text": "Not so for Nelson. He wasn&#39;t rich enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 125544.0,
      "end_time": 129515.0,
      "text": "and not so for his three-year-old son, who he discovered a year later"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 129514.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132756.0,
      "text": "also had HIV."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 132756.0,
      "end_time": 136176.0,
      "text": "Nelson decided to become a treatment activist"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 136176.0,
      "end_time": 138304.0,
      "text": "and join up with other groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138305.0,
      "end_time": 144648.0,
      "text": "In 2002, they were facing a different battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 144648.0,
      "end_time": 149363.0,
      "text": "Prices for ARVs, the drugs needed to treat HIV,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 149363.0,
      "end_time": 153760.0,
      "text": "cost about 12,000 [dollars] per patient per year."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 153760.0,
      "end_time": 156285.0,
      "text": "The patents on those drugs were held"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 156285.0,
      "end_time": 162550.0,
      "text": "by a number of Western pharmaceutical companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 162560.0,
      "end_time": 164977.0,
      "text": "that were not necessarily willing"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 164977.0,
      "end_time": 168218.0,
      "text": "to make those patents available."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 168218.0,
      "end_time": 170390.0,
      "text": "When you have a patent, you can exclude"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 170390.0,
      "end_time": 175119.0,
      "text": "anyone else from making, from producing or making"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 175119.0,
      "end_time": 178117.0,
      "text": "low-cost versions, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 178117.0,
      "end_time": 181692.0,
      "text": "available of those medications."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 181693.0,
      "end_time": 185954.0,
      "text": "Clearly this led to patent wars breaking out"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 185954.0,
      "end_time": 188912.0,
      "text": "all over the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 188912.0,
      "end_time": 192573.0,
      "text": "Luckily, those patents did not exist everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 192573.0,
      "end_time": 194965.0,
      "text": "There were countries that did not recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 194965.0,
      "end_time": 197884.0,
      "text": "pharmaceutical product patents, such as India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 197884.0,
      "end_time": 200404.0,
      "text": "and Indian pharmaceutical companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 200405.0,
      "end_time": 204364.0,
      "text": "started to produce so-called generic versions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 204364.0,
      "end_time": 208831.0,
      "text": "low-cost copies of antiretroviral medicines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 208831.0,
      "end_time": 212128.0,
      "text": "and make them available in the developing world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 212128.0,
      "end_time": 214844.0,
      "text": "and within a year the price had come down"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 214844.0,
      "end_time": 218630.0,
      "text": "from 10,000 dollars per patient per year"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 218630.0,
      "end_time": 221132.0,
      "text": "to 350 dollars per patient per year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 221132.0,
      "end_time": 224648.0,
      "text": "and today that same triple pill cocktail"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 224648.0,
      "end_time": 227484.0,
      "text": "is available for 60 dollars per patient per year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 227484.0,
      "end_time": 230848.0,
      "text": "and of course that started to have an enormous effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 230848.0,
      "end_time": 233937.0,
      "text": "on the number of people who could afford access"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 233937.0,
      "end_time": 235427.0,
      "text": "to those medicines."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 235427.0,
      "end_time": 238500.0,
      "text": "Treatment programs became possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 238500.0,
      "end_time": 241119.0,
      "text": "funding became available, and the number of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 241119.0,
      "end_time": 247880.0,
      "text": "on antiretroviral drugs started to increase very rapidly."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 247880.0,
      "end_time": 250593.0,
      "text": "Today, eight million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 250593.0,
      "end_time": 253709.0,
      "text": "have access to antiretroviral drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 253709.0,
      "end_time": 257691.0,
      "text": "Thirty-four million are infected with HIV."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 257690.0,
      "end_time": 259690.0,
      "text": "Never has this number been so high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 259690.0,
      "end_time": 260932.0,
      "text": "but actually this is good news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 260932.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263565.0,
      "text": "because what it means is people stop dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 263565.0,
      "end_time": 265885.0,
      "text": "People who have access to these drugs stop dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 265885.0,
      "end_time": 267221.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 267221.0,
      "end_time": 270500.0,
      "text": "They also stop passing on the virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 270500.0,
      "end_time": 273667.0,
      "text": "This is fairly recent science that has shown that."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273667.0,
      "end_time": 276323.0,
      "text": "What that means is we have the tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 276323.0,
      "end_time": 280800.0,
      "text": "to break the back of this epidemic."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 280800.0,
      "end_time": 285349.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s the problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 285349.0,
      "end_time": 287215.0,
      "text": "Well, things have changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 287215.0,
      "end_time": 291420.0,
      "text": "First of all, the rules have changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291430.0,
      "end_time": 296974.0,
      "text": "Today, all countries are obliged to provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 296974.0,
      "end_time": 301496.0,
      "text": "patents for pharmaceuticals that last at least 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 301496.0,
      "end_time": 304431.0,
      "text": "This is as a result of the intellectual property rules"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 304432.0,
      "end_time": 306780.0,
      "text": "of the World Trade Organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 306780.0,
      "end_time": 309958.0,
      "text": "So what India did is no longer possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 309959.0,
      "end_time": 315296.0,
      "text": "Second, the practice of patent-holding companies have changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 315296.0,
      "end_time": 319680.0,
      "text": "Here you see the patent practices"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 319680.0,
      "end_time": 323769.0,
      "text": "before the World Trade Organization&#39;s rules, before &#39;95,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 323769.0,
      "end_time": 326154.0,
      "text": "before antiretroviral drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 326154.0,
      "end_time": 328854.0,
      "text": "This is what you see today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 328854.0,
      "end_time": 331542.0,
      "text": "and this is in developing countries, so what that means is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 331542.0,
      "end_time": 333965.0,
      "text": "unless we do something deliberate"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 333965.0,
      "end_time": 336347.0,
      "text": "and unless we do something now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 336348.0,
      "end_time": 341464.0,
      "text": "we will very soon be faced with another drug price crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 341464.0,
      "end_time": 343684.0,
      "text": "because new drugs are developed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 343684.0,
      "end_time": 347460.0,
      "text": "new drugs go to market, but these medicines are patented"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 347460.0,
      "end_time": 350115.0,
      "text": "in a much wider range of countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 350115.0,
      "end_time": 354752.0,
      "text": "So unless we act, unless we do something today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 354752.0,
      "end_time": 358684.0,
      "text": "we will soon be faced [with] what some have termed"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 358684.0,
      "end_time": 361728.0,
      "text": "the treatment time bomb."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 361728.0,
      "end_time": 366587.0,
      "text": "It isn&#39;t only the number of drugs that are patented."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 366587.0,
      "end_time": 369370.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s something else that can really scare"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 369370.0,
      "end_time": 371211.0,
      "text": "generic manufacturers away."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 371211.0,
      "end_time": 375212.0,
      "text": "This shows you a patent landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 375212.0,
      "end_time": 378896.0,
      "text": "This is the landscape of one medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 378896.0,
      "end_time": 381497.0,
      "text": "So you can imagine that if you are a generic company"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 381497.0,
      "end_time": 383490.0,
      "text": "about to decide whether to invest"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 383490.0,
      "end_time": 386626.0,
      "text": "in the development of this product, unless you know"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 386626.0,
      "end_time": 389128.0,
      "text": "that the licenses to these patents"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 389129.0,
      "end_time": 391627.0,
      "text": "are actually going to be available,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 391627.0,
      "end_time": 394679.0,
      "text": "you will probably choose to do something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 394679.0,
      "end_time": 398611.0,
      "text": "Again, deliberate action is needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 398612.0,
      "end_time": 401900.0,
      "text": "So surely"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 401900.0,
      "end_time": 404936.0,
      "text": "if a patent pool could be established"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 404936.0,
      "end_time": 408996.0,
      "text": "to ramp up the production of military airplanes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 408997.0,
      "end_time": 412531.0,
      "text": "we should be able to do something similar"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 412531.0,
      "end_time": 416238.0,
      "text": "to tackle the HIV/AIDS epidemic."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 416238.0,
      "end_time": 418301.0,
      "text": "And we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 418301.0,
      "end_time": 423690.0,
      "text": "In 2010, UNITAID established the Medicines Patent Pool"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 423690.0,
      "end_time": 427173.0,
      "text": "for HIV."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 427173.0,
      "end_time": 428802.0,
      "text": "And this is how it works:"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 428802.0,
      "end_time": 432473.0,
      "text": "Patent holders, inventors"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 432473.0,
      "end_time": 436318.0,
      "text": "that develop new medicines"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 436318.0,
      "end_time": 438883.0,
      "text": "patent those inventions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 438884.0,
      "end_time": 440635.0,
      "text": "but make those patents available"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 440635.0,
      "end_time": 443608.0,
      "text": "to the Medicines Patent Pool. The Medicines Patent Pool"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 443608.0,
      "end_time": 447423.0,
      "text": "then license those out to whoever needs access to those patents."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 447423.0,
      "end_time": 449990.0,
      "text": "That can be generic manufacturers."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 449990.0,
      "end_time": 452912.0,
      "text": "It can also be not-for-profit drug development agencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 452912.0,
      "end_time": 454388.0,
      "text": "for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 454389.0,
      "end_time": 456903.0,
      "text": "Those manufacturers can then sell those medicines"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 456903.0,
      "end_time": 461952.0,
      "text": "at much lower cost to people who need access to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 461952.0,
      "end_time": 464524.0,
      "text": "to treatment programs that need access to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 464524.0,
      "end_time": 468700.0,
      "text": "They pay royalties over the sales to the patent holders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 468700.0,
      "end_time": 479290.0,
      "text": "so they are remunerated for sharing their intellectual property."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 479290.0,
      "end_time": 483870.0,
      "text": "There is one key difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 483870.0,
      "end_time": 486447.0,
      "text": "with the airplane patent pool."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 486447.0,
      "end_time": 491364.0,
      "text": "The Medicines Patent Pool is a voluntary mechanism."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 491364.0,
      "end_time": 494796.0,
      "text": "The airplane patent holders were not left a choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 494796.0,
      "end_time": 496436.0,
      "text": "whether they&#39;d license their patents or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 496436.0,
      "end_time": 498640.0,
      "text": "They were forced to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 498640.0,
      "end_time": 502562.0,
      "text": "That is something that the Medicines Patent Pool cannot do."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 502562.0,
      "end_time": 505914.0,
      "text": "It relies on the willingness of pharmaceutical companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 505914.0,
      "end_time": 509484.0,
      "text": "to license their patents and make them available"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 509484.0,
      "end_time": 514240.0,
      "text": "for others to use."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 514240.0,
      "end_time": 519188.0,
      "text": "Today, Nelson Otwoma is healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 519188.0,
      "end_time": 523170.0,
      "text": "He has access to antiretroviral drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 523171.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526948.0,
      "text": "His son will soon be 14 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 526948.0,
      "end_time": 529518.0,
      "text": "Nelson is a member of the expert advisory group"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 529518.0,
      "end_time": 531977.0,
      "text": "of the Medicines Patent Pool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 531977.0,
      "end_time": 534780.0,
      "text": "and he told me not so long ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 534780.0,
      "end_time": 539619.0,
      "text": "\"Ellen, we rely in Kenya and in many other countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 539619.0,
      "end_time": 543180.0,
      "text": "on the Medicines Patent Pool to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 543180.0,
      "end_time": 548530.0,
      "text": "that new medicines also become available to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 548530.0,
      "end_time": 553919.0,
      "text": "that new medicines, without delay, become available to us.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 553919.0,
      "end_time": 557278.0,
      "text": "And this is no longer fantasy."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 557278.0,
      "end_time": 561757.0,
      "text": "Already, I&#39;ll give you an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 561757.0,
      "end_time": 565214.0,
      "text": "In August of this year, the United States drug agency"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 565215.0,
      "end_time": 569164.0,
      "text": "approved a new four-in-one AIDS medication."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 569164.0,
      "end_time": 571869.0,
      "text": "The company, Gilead, that holds the patents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 571869.0,
      "end_time": 576105.0,
      "text": "has licensed the intellectual property to the Medicines Patent Pool."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 576105.0,
      "end_time": 580320.0,
      "text": "The pool is already working today, two months later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 580320.0,
      "end_time": 583137.0,
      "text": "with generic manufacturers to make sure that this product"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 583137.0,
      "end_time": 586286.0,
      "text": "can go to market at low cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 586286.0,
      "end_time": 589695.0,
      "text": "where and when it is needed. This is unprecedented."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 589696.0,
      "end_time": 591636.0,
      "text": "This has never been done before."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 591636.0,
      "end_time": 595355.0,
      "text": "The rule is about a 10-year delay for a new product"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 595355.0,
      "end_time": 598326.0,
      "text": "to go to market in developing countries, if at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 598326.0,
      "end_time": 602359.0,
      "text": "This has never been seen before."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 602359.0,
      "end_time": 605863.0,
      "text": "Nelson&#39;s expectations are very high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 605863.0,
      "end_time": 610132.0,
      "text": "and quite rightly so. He and his son will need access"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 610132.0,
      "end_time": 613221.0,
      "text": "to the next generation of antiretrovirals"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 613221.0,
      "end_time": 616328.0,
      "text": "and the next, throughout their lifetime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 616328.0,
      "end_time": 621600.0,
      "text": "so that he and many others in Kenya and other countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 621600.0,
      "end_time": 625438.0,
      "text": "can continue to live healthy, active lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 625438.0,
      "end_time": 628658.0,
      "text": "Now we count on the willingness of drug companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 628658.0,
      "end_time": 631280.0,
      "text": "to make that happen. We count on those companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 631280.0,
      "end_time": 634699.0,
      "text": "that understand that it is in the interest, not only in the interest"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 634700.0,
      "end_time": 637884.0,
      "text": "of the global good, but also in their own interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 637884.0,
      "end_time": 643598.0,
      "text": "to move from conflict to collaboration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 643598.0,
      "end_time": 646478.0,
      "text": "and through the Medicines Patent Pool they can make that happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 646479.0,
      "end_time": 649875.0,
      "text": "They can also choose not to do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 649875.0,
      "end_time": 656860.0,
      "text": "but those that go down that road may end up"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 656860.0,
      "end_time": 659100.0,
      "text": "in a similar situation the Wright brothers ended up with"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 659100.0,
      "end_time": 662843.0,
      "text": "early last century, facing forcible measures"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 662844.0,
      "end_time": 668260.0,
      "text": "by government. So they&#39;d better jump now."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 668260.0,
      "end_time": 671363.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}